English:
Huh? You found something?
What is it? That trashy old rag?
Chinese:
嗯？有找到什麼嗎？
什麼啊？好花俏的破布。
Korean:
……응? 뭔가 찾았어?
뭐야? 그 엄청 화려한 천은?
German:
Wie? Du hast etwas gefunden?
Was denn? Den alten Lumpen da?

English:
Why are these in here? And how long are you gonna
hold 'em for? Put those away!
Chinese:
為、為什麼會有這種鬼東西啦！？
你、你要拿到什麼時候！快點收起來啦！！
Korean:
왜, 왜 이런 게 들어 있는 거야!?
어, 언제까지 쥐고 있을 거야! 빨리 넣어!!
German:
Wieso sind die denn da drin? Und wie lange willst
du sie noch in der Hand halten? Tu die weg!
